# ABOUT BEHZAD SECTION

Section Title:

About Behzad Ghofranian

Content:

Over 20 years of experience in financial oversight, budgeting systems, and operational controls within a nationally recognized financial organization.

I work daily with accountants reviewing budgets, vendor contracts, expenditures, and financial reporting processes to support transparency, compliance, and accountability.

I also taught for 15 years, bringing strong communication, integrity, and responsibility to every leadership role.

Layout requirements:

Two-column layout

Left column:
Text content

Right column:
Profile photo placeholder

Image location:

/assets/images/profile.jpg

Image must scale responsively.

---

# WHY THIS SITE EXISTS

Section Title:

Why This Site Exists

Content:

Our community has experienced increased assessments, special insurance assessments, and major projects requiring clearer cost transparency.

This site was created to help residents better understand budgets, project costs, and how association funds are being used through summary analysis and supporting information.

The site provides:

- project cost breakdowns
- budget analysis
- contract summaries
- visual documentation of major projects

---

# COMMUNITY PRIORITIES SECTION

Section Title:

Community Priorities

Display items as cards or icon list.

Items:

Full cost breakdowns before major project approvals

Competitive vendor bidding and contract oversight

Clearer budgets and reserve planning

Timely access to official records as required by law

Independent and balanced board representation

Protection of long-term property values

Layout:

Grid layout

Desktop:
3 columns

Tablet:
2 columns

Mobile:
1 column

Each item should include an icon or simple visual marker.

---

# SPANISH SUMMARY SECTION

Section Title:

Resumen en Español

Content:

Más de 20 años de experiencia en supervisión financiera, control presupuestario y procesos administrativos en una organización financiera reconocida.

Trabajo diariamente con contadores revisando presupuestos, contratos con proveedores y reportes financieros para promover transparencia, cumplimiento y responsabilidad.

También fui profesor durante 15 años, aportando comunicación clara e integridad a cada rol de liderazgo.

Subsection Title:

Prioridades

Items:

Desglose claro de costos antes de aprobar proyectos

Evaluación competitiva de proveedores

Mejor planificación presupuestaria y de reservas

Acceso oportuno a registros oficiales según la ley

Representación equilibrada e independiente

Protección del valor de las propiedades

